# Recommender — <project-name>


**Problem statement:** Increase relevant content discovery and conversions through personalized recommendations.


**Primary metrics:** CTR, conversion rate, revenue per user, recall@K / NDCG@K (offline).


**Data sources:**
- User-item interaction logs (clicks, views, purchases)
- Catalog metadata (item ids, categories, price)
- User profile data (demographics, preferences)


**Validation:** Time-aware train/test split (e.g., last 7–14 days as holdout); use session-level splits for session-based models.


**Baseline:** Popularity-based recommendations or simple collaborative filtering (item-item).


**Deployment:** Batch top-K generation + real-time reranking when necessary.
